column16: Edwin Encarnacion grounds into a double play, second baseman Rougned Odor to shortstop Elvis Andrus to first baseman Joey Gallo.   Jason Kipnis out at 2nd.
Jose Ramirez flies out to center fielder Delino DeShields.
Jason Kipnis singles on a ground ball to right fielder Shin-Soo Choo.
Francisco Lindor flies out to left fielder Nomar Mazara.
Bradley Zimmer doubles (8) on a sharp line drive to left fielder Nomar Mazara.   Roberto Perez scores.
Roberto Perez doubles (5) on a sharp line drive to center fielder Carlos Gomez.   Carlos Santana scores.
Carlos Santana doubles (17) on a sharp line drive to center fielder Carlos Gomez.   Edwin Encarnacion scores.  Carlos Santana advances to 3rd, on a throwing error by second baseman Rougned Odor.
Edwin Encarnacion doubles (8) on a line drive to right fielder Shin-Soo Choo.
